PrecisAppointment of GUY GIGUÈRE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Public Service Staff Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years; and order that GUY GIGUÈRE be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective June 29, 1998.

precis:
Appointment of GUY GIGUÈRE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of
the Public Service Staff Relations Board to hold office during good
behaviour for a period of three years; and order that GUY GIGUÈRE be
deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the
Public Service Superannuation Act, effective June 29, 1998.
